    USER_ON_START                   TMP$C2729A
    USER_ON_EXTDS                   TMP$C2729A
    SAME_ATTACH                     Y

    USER_ON_START                   TMP$C2729A
    USER_ON_EXTDS                   TMP$C2729B
    SAME_ATTACH                     N
  """
}
